{"tid":2227803,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點樣可以對阿媽好d？","createTime":"2020-10-03T05:41:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-08T10:03:25.000Z","uid":209057,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"24ab926f565773d53325e30d961a0b83902c791e","tid":2227803,"uid":209057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"我阿媽脾氣真係好暴躁，唔知係咪佢更年期到<br />\n講下笑都會嬲成日。我知佢都有自己難處，所以已經儘量乜都就曬佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n琴日一家人出街，佢出街黑口黑面，嘢又唔講，嬲左成日就係因為阿爸大前日笑佢...<br />\n<br />\n我平時壓力已經好大，自己都處理唔自己ge壓力，宜家仲要handle埋佢d負面情緒。<br />\n好想對阿媽態度好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢一鬧我，我同佢就好似兩個炸彈咁，睇下邊個爆先<br />\n<br />\n點樣可以改善下我同佢關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔想再係咁<br />\n好辛苦"},{"pid":"d8b8896b12fbe7d424351e939ee5334653fb45c1","tid":2227803,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:49:53.000Z","msg":"同佢傾下<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5380f95139eea1ae8140334c5d5acb1ffc2b6c69","tid":2227803,"uid":82450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:52:45.000Z","msg":"唔好講嘢 各有各做"},{"pid":"f9c8c61b464c6343acd5daa235e9559779332f2e","tid":2227803,"uid":211923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:34:27.000Z","msg":"唔好一齊住"},{"pid":"05ef5114908ff27e1e2f5958a751a8d1477a46da","tid":2227803,"uid":313313,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T14:41:05.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 成日同呀媽嘈 呀媽又係好易嬲<br />\n但好彩我呀爸做中間人 會幫我地解圍 <br />\n嘈完會同我地傾下 叫大家包容遷就下<br />\n多數過左一日/一日半就冇事"},{"pid":"ea46f781a398181f338f630c2beda17864344b43","tid":2227803,"uid":12909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"24ab926f565773d53325e30d961a0b83902c791e","tid":2227803,"uid":209057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T05:41:34.000Z","msg":"我阿媽脾氣真係好暴躁，唔知係咪佢更年期到<br />\n講下笑都會嬲成日。我知佢都有自己難處，所以已經儘量乜都就曬佢<img src=\"/asset